:"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 17:8","book":"Rev","chapter":17,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" each different from the other."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dn 7:17","book":"Dan","chapter":7,"verse":17},{"label":"Rv 13:1","book":"Rev","chapter":13,"verse":1},{"label":"Rv 17:8","book":"Rev","chapter":17,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:7:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“The first was like a lion "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 4:7","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 25:9","book":"Jer","chapter":25,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 13:2","book":"Rev","chapter":13,"verse":2,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" but had eagle’s wings. I continued watching until its wings were torn off. It was lifted up from the ground, set on its feet like a man, and given a human mind."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 4:7","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":7},{"label":"Jr 25:9","book":"Jer","chapter":25,"verse":9},{"label":"Rv 13:2","book":"Rev","chapter":13,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:7:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Suddenly, another beast appeared, a second one, that looked like a bear. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 13:2","book":"Rev","chapter":13,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" It was raised up on one side, with three ribs in its mouth between its teeth. It was told, ‘Get up! Gorge yourself on flesh.’"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rv 13:2","book":"Rev","chapter":13,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Dan:7:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“After this, while I was watching, suddenly another beast appeared. It was like a leopard "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hab 1:8","book":"Hab","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 13:2","book":"Rev","chapter":13,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" with four wings of a bird on its back. It had four heads, "},{"kin